# Authorship

Engin Atik is the sole author on all papers, documents, and publications produced in this project.

**Never** add Claude, AI assistants, or any other entity as a co-author, contributor, or affiliate.

```kleis
// ✅ Correct
define paper_authors = [Author("Engin Atik", "1")]

// ❌ Wrong — never do this
define paper_authors = [Author("Engin Atik", "1"), Author("Claude", "2")]
```
